Pulse Yoga

	Philosophy

		-
			Pulse yoga is the practice of focusing on, manipulating, interpreting, and
			contextualizing internal physical sensations as an aid to meditation.
		-

	Principles

		Pulse

			-
				One's pulse, in various areas of the body, is the nominal and primary subject of
				pulse meditation.

				In pulse meditation, one may envision, and metaphorically interpret, the sensation
				of their pulse as waves of energy being emitted or received.
